- Why are you taking this risk? - I had to warn you.

918
01:24:12,525 --> 01:24:14,980
啊，親愛的上帝
My husband is alive.

919
01:24:16,320 --> 01:24:17,732
他還活著？
Dear God!

920
01:24:20,200 --> 01:24:21,481
