別亂說話，太太
Love has forced me to open my heart to another.

947
01:26:34,936 --> 01:26:36,845
那個教你說這些話的影子情人
Watch your tongue, woman!

948
01:26:37,063 --> 01:26:40,148
他在哪兒？
