很好
you will be easily found.

968
01:27:29,750 --> 01:27:30,414
從野蠻人那裏
Easily!

969
01:27:33,044 --> 01:27:34,835
我學會了耐心
From the savages

970
01:27:35,046 --> 01:27:37,584
海絲特·白蘭因.
I have learned patience,

971
01:27:38,216 --> 01:27:39,676
古蒂·高德威克，謝謝
Hester Prynne.

972
01:28:18,513 --> 01:28:20,506
