分離的痛苦影響了大家.
my father wore his own scarlet letteron the bosom ofhis soul.

1018
01:32:21,415 --> 01:32:24,950
我是一個非常難纏的孩子
The pain of their separation must have affected us all.

1019
01:32:25,169 --> 01:32:27,839
為解相思之苦
I was a troublesome child.

1020
01:32:28,882 --> 01:32:31,004
父親帶著約翰尼去野外以求擺脫孤獨
My father ached formy mother,

1021
01:32:31,258 --> 01:32:34,628
他們想在英國人和印第安人之間
and filled his loneliness in the wilds with Johnny.

1022
01:32:34,846 --> 01:32:36,305
架起一座橋樑
They struggled

1023
01:32:36,514 --> 01:32:38,258
並且努力維護著這個夢想
to keep alive their  dream

1024
01:32:38,517 --> 01:32:39,976
約翰尼
of building a bridge between English and Indian.

1025
01:32:41,771 --> 01:32:42,934
他們離鎮子為什麼這麼近
Johnny,

1026
01:32:44,065 --> 01:32:46,189
他們說，我們的人都睡了
why are they so close to town?

1027
01:32:46,818 --> 01:32:49,820
