They say our people have fallen asleep.

1028
01:32:50,489 --> 01:32:53,110
我很擔心
So they must remain awake for all of us.

1029
01:32:55,953 --> 01:32:57,199
會有戰爭嗎，阿瑟
I'm worried.

1030
01:32:57,872 --> 01:32:59,700
偉大的夢想破滅了，是嗎？
Is war coming?

1031
01:33:00,000 --> 01:33:02,918
他說的對
The great experiment is not working, is it?

1032
01:33:11,850 --> 01:33:13,048
如果真的有戰爭 如何阻止那些皈依的印第安人叛變
Yes, he's right.

1033
