寒冷的冬天，糧食欠收
What manner of signs?

1054
01:34:13,814 --> 01:34:16,305
鎮子裏有過多的信徒和外來人
The bad winter. The crop failures.

1055
01:34:16,942 --> 01:34:20,523
一些小小的不安分子
Far too many Quakers and foreigners in the town.

1056
